  "notes": "Live Shopify evidence that `Invoice error parity item` is just ordinary draftOrderCreate input data. The captured request submits quantity 2, SKU MAGIC-TITLE-NOT-CANNED, no shipping requirement, tags, and custom attributes; strict parity would have failed against the removed scenario-keyed canned #D1 draft path."
